Bootstrap: docker
From: clearlinux/python:3.9.4

%post
    swupd bundle-add --quiet python-extras
    swupd clean --all

%test
    python -c 'import scipy; print("SciPy version: " + scipy.__version__)'

%environment
    export LC_ALL=C

%runscript
    python

%help
    Based on the official Clear Linux python:3.9.4 Docker image with the latest python-extras bundle installed. OpenBLAS is included. Packages installed: scipy, numpy, pandas, matplotlib, scikit-learn, dask, and others.
